<br>
Well I'm all for getting rid of Saddam, but not for war on his *country* that will cost thousands of lives :/<br>
<br>
Some things need to be remembered:<br>
<br>
1) In the first GulF War 200,000 iraqi troops were massacred, and yes MASSACRED is the appropriate word because it was a military pushover and wipe out on a truly grand scale (due to the skill and equipment of the allies). That is not to say it was a &quot;war crime&quot;, but merely a totally obliteration with little retaliation. You didnt see many images of the effects, did you? Nice sanitized news coverage for the most part. Carpet bombing, napalming, fuel air bombs, cluster weapons on stupid bloody straight defence lines and armoured clomuns or fleeing units = carnage. yes a fair number of those killed would have been guilty of war crimes, but most were just poor slobs conscripted into the army. I hope the military *threat* forces Saddam and co to leave or be pushed out, but war would be vile. <br>
Shoot THOSE specific fuggers at the top if you have to, not a whole country.<br>
<br>
2) Who put Saddam Hussein, the Ayatollah Homenei and other various loonies in power across the world in the first place, hm?<br>
<br>
3) Is it REALLY Saddam Hussein? With amount of stand ins he's had, who knows if hes alive, or merely a &quot;bogeyman&quot; used by clever manipulators?<br>
<br>
4) yeah I could believe the SOB would have backed terrorist grousp over the world in revenge for 1991. Hm, though he's one of the few moderate Muslim leaders left...he and the extremists don't usually get on, one reason folk think he was left as a sort of check to them. If he goes, will the whole arab world go extremist?<br>
<br>
5) Like America doesnt have weapons of mass destruction, duh? While the Army almost certaily has got rid of chem and bio weapons, other US agencies have certainly been a tad shady about such stuff. *cough, CIA recruiting folk with bio-science degress...* Most militaries stopped working with chem and particularly bio weapons are finding out how nasty they were (stupid civilain scientists had been fed lines for ages about them not being &quot;that bad&quot; and took it hook line and sinker). For tactical, security, safety and just plain common sense and morality reasons, most military don't want the damn things. Political security departments of just about any government tend to be psychopathic @#%$ by definition (paranoid schizophrenics) and are as untrustworthy as terminally syphilitic homicidal religious maniacs :&gt;<br>
  The Russians had a vast chem/bio weapon system as it was cheaper than nuclear, and most of it was designed to take out the Chinese, whom they had serious fears about<br>
(oh CHina is the SECOND world Super Power today ya know). With the end of the Soviet Union, a lot of that technology, some materials, and critically, the personel, dispersed.<br>
  The UN weapons inspectors coudln't find some of the stuff Saddam MAY have, no matter how hard they look, as it can be made in a small mobile truck. <br>
  Real secret and big trouble with NBC weapons has always been storage, and critically, the delivery systems. The Son of Star Wars wanted by Bush Junior is the biggest load of b*lls, because the greatest danger to a nation in regrds to NBC weapons hasnt been ballistic missles for decades, it's CONTRABAND smuggling of them into a nation. hence terrorists with them scares the bejezus out of folk because they are loonies with little control, and the ability and will to use them. Interceptor systems wont stop a loony dumping Sarin from a rooftop.<br>
<br>
6) NBC weapons are of less threat to the military than to civilians. Only a fool woudl use them on a military action because retalition would be total and the effects minimal. As Saddam showed on the Kurds though, they are terrible on civilians (also on stupid religious maniacs like the Iranians who sent massed wave attacks against prepared Iraqi positions, making the battles of World War1 look tame)<br>
<br>
7) Terrorism is the new COMMIE RED THREAT! and using that America is degenerating into a police state, or would you deny a ton of the liberties Americans, quite rightly fought for, are being quashed, and maybe abused by the state against its very citizens? Dont you have a sneaking feeling that the new homeland security agency maybe a new Gestapo?<br>
  It's also a question of WAG THE DOG. Ignore the falling economy, lower wages etc, here's a Jew/commie/terrorist/Republican/Christian/Moslem/infidel/Loyalist/Fascist/Nazi/Russki/Chink/scapegoat to blame and abuse and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>ignore the man behind the curtain!</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
 All that stuff seriously reminds me of Babylon5, the Night Watch etc..it doesn't, don't it? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Want to fix half the problems in the world? Easy, new UN resolution: THE LEADERS OF ANY STATE SHALL BE HELD RESPONSIBLE FOR ACTIONS COMMITED BY THEIR GOVERNMENTS IN THEIR NAME, AND WILL BE TRIED FOR CRIMES AGAINST HUMANITY IF NECESSARY.<br>
 Bet ya that will NEVER get passed, but would stop most of the bullsh*t form ANY nation, if the leaders knew they PERSONALLY would get shot for any crap. The lack of fear of retribution allows many politicans to be disgusting vermin REGARDLESS OF THE NATONALITY. Hey, at worst they get to retire with fat pensions from the companies they have done sweet deals for, boo hoo! Bastrds should be jailed for *life* and all their assests, including those owned by family members who profited from their relative's crookery, should be<br>
confiscated and put back into the national treasury.<br>
